videos.description: Kansas' Lagerald Vick creates space to knock down the open 3-pointer to help pad the lead for the Jayhawks.
videos.headline: Vick hits open trey

videos.description: Kansas' Mitch Lightfoot makes the block off the backboard which leads to the Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk alley-oop dunk.
videos.headline: Kansas turns block into an alley-oop

videos.description: Kansas' Mitch Lightfoot follows up the missed shot with a strong putback dunk and Devonte' Graham throws up the three-quarter court lob to Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk for the dunk.
videos.headline: Lightfoot and Mykhailiuk spur the offense
